<p><br />
<li>Rake: Damage increased. Energy cost reduced if Rake fails.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Ravage: Damage increased. Energy cost reduced if Ravage fails.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Regrowth: Mana cost and heal amount increased.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Rip: Energy cost and duration increased.  Damage reduced.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Roar: No longer locks out other Roar abilities for five seconds.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Shred: Damage increased. Energy cost reduced if Shred fails.<br />
