<p><br />
<li>Swipe: Damage slightly increased.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Thorns: Mana cost and damage increased.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Hit Points and Attack Power at lower levels has been increased while in Bear form.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Attack Rate is faster while in Cat form.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Druids in shapeshifted form can now gather herbs and skin creatures.  <br />
<p><br />
<li>The camera now changes appropriately for shapeshifted forms.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Druids under the effects of Enrage are now considered in combat.<br />
<p><br />
<li>Attack power has been lowered for Druids in their normal caster form.<br />
</ul><br />
